Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想大哭一场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时也不是孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远的梦想在闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它找回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把双眼闭上便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中的一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算留下伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕 现在是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃 Step by Step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓着梦想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常也和你一起向明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续前进 Step by Step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想坚信着 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想向着天空大声呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧着 in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配着遥远星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再次成为救世主,展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二星界是有趣的冒险世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里我们要把被沙漠化了的世界恢复原本翠绿的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从奥巴鸟手上夺回星石的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次向基拿基拿山进发了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十一话\N炎热的山下起雪来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高,好高…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基拿基拿山可以说是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二星界的象征的神圣的山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山顶上,有座叫雪石的奇怪石像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把星石放到石像的肚脐穴内的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山便会下起雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪溶出来的水会令第二星界恢复一片翠绿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪闪发亮的基拿基拿山吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,我一定会令雪下起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊!见到整座基拿基拿山了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草菇啊,草菇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的地方,怎么爬上去啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下也有不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,象先生的鼻子很长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡先生,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,艾利芬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送渡他们一程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个很好的飞行旅程呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他办法的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!快闪开…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火子,火子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何会在这里的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里是我的自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又想打我的剑主意吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这是雪石像?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话,立即把星石放进肚脐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点,快点,钢铁兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡他们已去到那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种冻到头痛的快感真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用尽千方百计才完成的这个沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能让那渡把它恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草莓蜜瓜冰还未完成吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草莓蜜瓜冰还未…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等我啊,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道什么叫友情和帮助吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一、二、三!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真累呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起此事,你看看那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个肚脐很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道那颗不是星石吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会有这个可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗绝对是星石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对,绝…绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是星石,真真正正的星石!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石像说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是救世主渡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把星石带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话你便用基拿基拿山的冰河之水把那石清洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话,石头便会变为真正的星石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是真正的救世主的话,那便可以做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这个第二星界的波士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法鲁战王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二星界的波士?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了各位,但是请你们看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刨冰,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是用基拿基拿山最后的冰河造成的刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,最后的冰被…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很想吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你们便不能完成真正的星石了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗憾之余,你们更会在此消失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,带走星石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒那家伙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古怪的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好,被你们看到了我正面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,看了的话更不能饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每流进一步,便更接近地狱的入口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话,便会如他所说一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信着,相信着石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信石头?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信着,相信着石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信石头…石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家跟着我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?渡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在想什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超有型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔,火子,我们也去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样去啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔和火子,首先捉紧这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉紧了又怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉紧了的话便一起飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要自己走到生命的尽头吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃得还真快的家伙们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,火美子!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里!哈哈,真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?师傅呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,师傅!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何我要遇上这种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,不要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,总言之大家都没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样也叫没事的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去,被活埋也只是时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好尝尝沙地狱的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信这石头,绝对有出口的,绝对有的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了成功了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔?这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要相信石头?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,我的确是这样听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你便跳进流沙里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那石害我这么惨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!看,有光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是冰的洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这里是地下水,冻结了的冰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这也是冰河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,也许溶掉这些冰,再用来清洗星石话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法鲁战王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位,你们已逃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这么多冰真令人耐不住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刨冰,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,是现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,趁现在把星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!你想干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要帮手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点本事呢,可是这又怎样!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们打算把星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你们成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,师傅他们有危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟打我?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话,便让你看看帝皇司令官的真正力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变形了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓一跳之余这个又怎样啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超特大鳄鱼飞战!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞吧,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熔岩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,冰被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去全部会溶掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,要保护这些冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好,不叫战神丸来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔变成厨菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溶吧溶吧,全部溶掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在全部溶掉之前要再吃一次,现在已确实的胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,比起这个,冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保护冰啊,龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙雷拳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,竟阻碍我最大的趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,超级巨炮攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是机会了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃草莓蜜瓜刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是空神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么是古拿玛来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点,渡,还有魔神在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,又是那部魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要大意,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部溶掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟有这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星界已不能恢复原状了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刨…刨冰,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才那大叔留下了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,火美子,不要再刨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最爱吃刨冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀!冷得头很痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干了什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便是真正的星石吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次刚刚好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪吧,下雪吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪降下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来第二星界也恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,就这个样子第三星界也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次是第三星界了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了? 这个胸口在驱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop! 已不能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你也一个劲儿地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油门不用放开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直踏着 Go!Go!Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:23:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是速度的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TONIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.81,0:23:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直望着的瞳孔涌上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜 MY LOVE

